{0 Tempo}

Tempo is the primary package of the project.

It exposes:
- {!module-Tempo.Core}: the canonical synchronous programming API
- {!module-Tempo.Constructs}: higher-level reactive operators built on the core
- {!module-Tempo.Observe}: tracing and runtime inspection helpers
- {!module-Tempo.Meta}: version and API-level metadata
- {!module-Tempo.Low_level}: advanced scheduler primitives for extension authors

See also:
- {!page-overview}
- {!page-runtime_layers}
- the dedicated `tempo-app` package for lightweight application structure
- the dedicated `tempo-jobs` package for external jobs on domains
- the dedicated `tempo-raylib` package for Raylib helpers
- the dedicated `tempo-fluidsynth` package for musical demos
